#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_array.rst:17
msgid ""
"Generic array which can contain several elements of any type, accessible "
"by a numerical index starting at 0. Negative indices can be used to count"
" from the back, like in Python (-1 is the last element, -2 the second to "
"last, etc.)."
msgstr "通用数组，可以包含多个任何类型的元素，可通过从0开始的数字索引进行访问。负索引可用于从后面进行计数，类似在Python中（-1是最后一个元素，-2是倒数第二个元素，依此类推）。"

